97PJ_INLINE(void) pj_stun_config_init(pj_stun_config *cfg,
98 pj_pool_factory *factory,
99 unsigned options,
100 pj_ioqueue_t *ioqueue,
101 pj_timer_heap_t *timer_heap)
102{
103 pj_bzero(cfg, sizeof(*cfg));
104
105 cfg->pf = factory;
106 cfg->options = options;
107 cfg->ioqueue = ioqueue;
108 cfg->timer_heap = timer_heap;
109 cfg->rto_msec = PJ_STUN_RTO_VALUE;
110 cfg->res_cache_msec = PJ_STUN_RES_CACHE_DURATION;
111 cfg->software_name = pj_str((char*)PJNATH_STUN_SOFTWARE_NAME);
112}
113
114
118PJ_INLINE(pj_status_t) pj_stun_config_check_valid(const pj_stun_config *cfg)
119{
120 PJ_ASSERT_RETURN(cfg->ioqueue && cfg->pf && cfg->timer_heap &&
121 cfg->rto_msec && cfg->res_cache_msec, PJ_EINVAL);
122 return PJ_SUCCESS;
123}
